1. Unzip "pizzashop-rs_1.0.zip" file and paste to App Server (5.2.1)  webapps folder (AS_HOME/repository/deployment/server/webapps)
2. Create api on ESB as per "config.xml"
3. Send following requests:
curl -v "http://10.100.0.33:8281/pizzashop/api/menu/pizza/all"

Response:
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json
Date: Thu, 06 Feb 2014 05:03:08 GMT
Server: WSO2-PassThrough-HTTP
Transfer-Encoding: chunked

